review_text: Nice little bike path for learning on a glider. And a fun dinosaur on springs to ride.
Great playground for kids. Too many judgy moms think they own the place...
Toddler bike path and two jungle gyms. Pretty well maintained, but the entry gate is a bit fiddly.
Lovely place to get out to.
Nice park for children
Not a lot of places to sit for adults great for kids though

(Translated by Google) We really like this park it is safe well fenced. There is a play module for children, one for adults (6-12 years old), there are swings for adults and children, a sandbox and a spring dinosaur. However the pit toilet would really need to be cleaned more often and it would be great to add a picnic table or two.

(Original)
Nous aimons beaucoup ce parc il est sécuritaire bien clôturé. Il y a un module de jeux pour les petits, un pour les grands (6-12 ans), il y a des balançoires pour grands et petits, un carré de sable ainsi qu'un dinosaure à ressort. Cependant la toilette sèche aurait vraiment besoin d'être nettoyé plus souvent et il serait très intéressant d'ajouter une ou deux tables à pique-nique.
